item.synopsis: Getting to the third level of zombies on "Call of Duty: Black Ops" seems easy, until you realize that it means that you have to actually survive the first two levels. Get to the third level of zombies on "Call of Duty: Black Ops" games with help from an expert in the art of digital warfare in this free video clip.
